title: Trekking to Tassie: Perth to Launceston ✔️
description: 4328 km later, seeing countless number of kangaroos, hours of sitting in the car, numerous slow caravan drivers, 7 apostles, 4 motels, 2 koalas, a giant galah, a dingo, an emu, a giant lobster and a camel we have made it to little old Launceston.
